org.webcurator.domain.model.core
Class TargetInstance

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.core.TargetInstance
All Implemented Interfaces:
InTrayResource, UserInTrayResource, Annotatable, HasOid, Overrideable, UserOwnable
public class TargetInstance
extends java.lang.Object
implements Annotatable, Overrideable, UserInTrayResource

A TargetInstance represents a particular harvest at a given date and time. It takes its initial details from a Target, but may be modified to change its profile overrides, etc.

getOverrides

public ProfileOverrides getOverrides()
Get the overrides for Hibernate ONLY. Application code should use the getProfileOverrides() method. KU 10-01-2008: because the TargetInstance does not "own" the profile overrides (they are notionally owned by the Target) there are problems when the target instance is deleted (the override may still be referenced). I have therefore changed the cascade option for hibernate from "all" to "save-update"
